# === Third-party extracted assets (NOT versioned — repo slim + license-safe) ===
# The extracted zip packs live only locally; ASSET_LOG.md records their source/license.
# Our ORIGINAL assets live in game/assets/ and are versioned.
assets_raw/
# The root asset .zip/.rar archives are ignored (already extracted to assets_raw/).
# assets_raw/lpc/ = stash LPC (dipindah dari .vscode/ per #232-4) — tercakup baris di atas.
# CATATAN: assets_publikasi/ (sprite turunan LPC + LICENSE/CREDITS) SENGAJA di-commit (CC-BY-SA).

